gamecore.entity

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • gamecore.entity.Entity

  • public final class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    The meat-and-potatoes of combat. Each Entity has a name, a set of attributes, a weapon slot, armor slots, an EntityType, and an Inventory.
    The only way to instantiate an Entity is through an EntityBuilder object.
    Author:
    Alex Chythlook
